metadata.name: Pixl Palace #1
metadata.description: Pixl Palaces are a staple within the Pixlverse land ownership system - these super rare items will be used to host businesses and social hubs within the Pixlverse. Unlike regular player homes these Palaces exist persistently within the open world and are viewable on the world map! Palaces offer incredible productive potential, hosting any form of enterprise you can imagine as we pioneer a Web3 revolution.
